{"title":"洛阳诗草","authors":["巴牧"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"洛阳诗草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙门山色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像青秀的海岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被洪流冲开！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那顶天的石峰呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在水上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搭起两座楼台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明净的伊水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一面镜子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好的照照吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙门，而今——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的美容犹在。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洛阳灯海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平原上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出现一片灯海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仲夏夜的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一泓清泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流入心怀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静的夜呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁的灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从海边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻走来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣赏着那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮晶晶的灯海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心中发出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多感慨："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，祖国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这无数盏灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像千万只"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微笑的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在向你表示："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强烈的爱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石佛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把云彩当袈裟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿成一串佛珠；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在陡峭的岩边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，静坐了千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看日月轮回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细听河流念经。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“阴狱渡”偶感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洛阳城南龙门渡口，有一“八节滩”，河水急湍多险，诗人白居易曾在这里兴工开凿“阴狱渡”，免除了渔船航行的苦难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在八节滩的岸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，映天的河流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白帆片片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声渔唱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是智慧的诗人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴工平浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开凿十里河滩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"免除了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔家的悲伤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伊河两岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农舍处处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地金黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭泣的河流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已是笑声朗朗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像渔家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年月月，在把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恩情歌唱。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}